---
title: PB&J Oatmeal with Honey, Peanuts & Dried Cherries
description: Name a breakfast more comforting or filling than a hot, hearty bowl of oatmeal (...we’ll wait). Ready to make it irresistible to kids and grown-ups alike? Add dried cherries, peanut butter, cherry jam, and honey to the mix—it’s the perfect formula for a yummy morning. The best part? This delicious, wholesome bowl comes together in a quick 15 minutes! After digging in, you’ll all be fueled up and ready to take on the day (and with more time to do it!).
